The Alex Jones Show

Wednesday January 14, 2009.

Jason Bermas holds down the Infowars command center while Alex is away. Jason talks with What Really Happened editor and GCN radio talks show host Mike Rivero. Jason also talks with retired CIA officer and political activist Ray McGovern and discusses the issues of the day and takes your calls.
